---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy" description="Privacy policy WandaSystems">
  <section class="pt-20 pb-32">
    <div class="container-content">
      <span class="badge mb-4 inline-block">Privacy</span>
      <h1 class="text-heading-1 mb-10 text-text-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-prose text-text-secondary">
        <h2 class="text-text-primary">1. Overview</h2>
        <p>
          This page explains how personal data is handled when you visit this website or contact WandaSystems.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-text-primary">2. Hosting and Logs</h2>
        <p>
          This website is statically hosted. Technical request data (for example IP address, browser metadata, timestamp)
          may be processed in server logs for security and stability purposes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-text-primary">3. Contact Requests</h2>
        <p>
          If you contact us via form or email, the submitted information is used to process your request and potential follow-up.
          Data is not sold and is not shared beyond what is required for communication and operations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-text-primary">4. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:wanda.devops@gmail.com" class="text-brand-gold hover:underline">wanda.devops@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
